info.description:
The guide providers: http://svt.se, http://tv4.se, http://tv3.se,
                     http://tv1000.se, http://viasat.se,
                     http://www.mtve.com, http://ztv.se,
                     http://tv8.se, http://eurosporttv.se
                     http://3plus.dk, http://sr.se,
                     http://tv.hd.se and http://kanal5.se

This grabber currently provides the following xmltv elements
channel
progamme (with title, start & stop time)
extra info (if available for a particular programme)
    desc
    episode-num
    category
    previously-shown
more info will be implemented when xmltv 0.6 finalizes
